I went back to my room with my head hanging.
That night, I was sitting alone at dinner in college when someone tapped me on the shoulder.
It was a second-year English student named James who introduced himself as a member of the conservative student union.
"I know who you are", he said kindly.
Unfortunately, it is what it is.
Anyone suspected of being a Tory is being bullied.
It's bad enough for me, but they know your father is close to Margaret Thatcher, so it's gonna be worse for you.
