"I prefer him to everyone else because of his great love for women and because he highlights our beauty", adds the former Duchess of Feria.
I like the colors he uses very much; they have a lot of light and emphasize the face.
The proportions are perfect.
Even the princess and fashion commentator Patricia della Giovampaola d'Arenberg cannot forget the first time she wore a Valentino.
When I was a teenager living in Italy, I dreamed of finally being old enough to wear one of his evening gowns...
